  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Setuna, aspiring to become the ultimate warrior, receives a new mission. Cutting down enemy after enemy, Setuna fights through countless battles to return home safely once again. A legendary tale spun by hamburgers, players take on the role of Setuna to etch their name into history.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Solo Anime-Style Hardcore Action Game]</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>~ Fight Your Way, Your Style ~</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Techniques Transform Mid-Action:</strong> Attacks change into different skills depending on your current action (Martial Arts Techniques).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unrestricted Action Flow:</strong> Cancel any motion at any time (\"Setuna Cancel\").</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Seamless Action Chain:</strong> Connect every move freely and fluidly at any timing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3507910/extras/9671fd99e74234ad7e5f75ce3d092e8a.poster.avif?t=1760867061\" width=574 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3507910/extras/9671fd99e74234ad7e5f75ce3d092e8a.webm?t=1760867061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3507910/extras/9671fd99e74234ad7e5f75ce3d092e8a.mp4?t=1760867061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dodge Without Stopping Attacks:</strong> Continue attack motions while nullifying enemy attacks (Attack Motion Dodge).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3507910/extras/9233eb945a47fede3bfc62b97c7a377f.poster.avif?t=1760867061\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3507910/extras/9233eb945a47fede3bfc62b97c7a377f.webm?t=1760867061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3507910/extras/9233eb945a47fede3bfc62b97c7a377f.mp4?t=1760867061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase art and decorate your base with it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3507910/extras/4d2e0f7432b0c6dd04487a9526d10ccd.avif?t=1760867061\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3507910/extras_big/4d2e0f7432b0c6dd04487a9526d10ccd.avif?t=1760867061 width=800 height=346 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >_____________________________________________________________</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Additional Notes</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No lock-on feature, no camera correction, no character rotation adjustment, and no range correction.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you'd like to change key configurations, please use Steam's controller settings or customize button layouts using gaming keyboards or mice.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game’s content may be used freely in videos or live streams by anyone without any restrictions.</p></li></ul>",
